  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>SilverMists are clo=
uds of
  microscopic nanomachines. Our knowledge of them comes from ancient stories
  &#8211; no SilverMists are known to exist today.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>The legends describ=
e SilverMists
  as a deadly menace that consumes anything in their paths. They even attack
  colonies, consuming all organic life and leaving behind a barren world
  ravaged by destruction.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>As they consume mat=
erials,
  SilverMist clouds grow until they reach sufficient size to split in two,
  forming a new nanocloud creature!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Ordinary weapons ar=
e only
  marginally effective against these threats. Rumour has it that Ion weapons
  are the best way to attack a SilverMist cloud.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
